目录也很繁杂的电子书，Pr...</q></div>真的\b好奇怪啊，我下了 PDF EXPERT 试用，字体渲染没有问题，不模糊，但是加载速度比 PREVIEW 和 SKIM 还慢……<br>发现现在加载速度最快且显示效果也很好的居然是 CHROME，无语了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/31/13161.jpg","floor":"#2-5","id":"1294723","time":"2017-12-1 21:18","userId":"mewing","userName":"mewing","userSign":"","message":"还有过这样的优惠啊……"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3417.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1286219","time":"2017-10-30 13:06","userId":"venusxx","userName":"Venusxx","userSign":"(xxsuneV)","message":"tora是什么鬼","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/77/257753.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1286230","time":"2017-10-30 14:24","userId":"257753","userName":"为了坚果","userSign":"","message":"某猫科小萌物。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/69/6912.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1286240","time":"2017-10-30 15:32","userId":"6912","userName":"tora","userSign":"","message":"就是我头像的名字"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/45/124586.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1286260","time":"2017-10-30 19:25","userId":"124586","userName":"用户","userSign":"(周黑鸭)","message":"用国产免费的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/93/259355.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1286296","time":"2017-10-30 21:41","userId":"259355","userName":"莉萝爱","userSign":"(在迷茫中前行(￣▽￣))","message":"之前有个卖软件的套装优惠，39刀买包括pdf expert在内的10个软件（不过已经结束了）。<br>不过感觉pdf expert 2.X的版本没以前1.X的好用，现在全屏上面始终会有一栏工具栏无法隐藏，不能沉浸阅读<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/17.gif\" smileid=\"56\" alt=\"(bgm40)\"><br>要是题主是学生党，用来看pdf作笔记学习的话，另外推荐个国产软件<a href=\"https://marginnote.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\"> margin note</a>，能划重点做笔记并整合成为思维导图，牛逼疯了（PS：我真的不是在打广告<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/70.gif\" smileid=\"109\" alt=\"(bgm93)\">）","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1286300","time":"2017-10-30 21:54","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"很好，这么牛逼的软件根本不在乎我们windows用户<img src=\"/img/smiles/